{
  "texts": [
    "If the treatments have an effect, in which labor market outcomes would they manifest?",
    "And how can we identify these impacts in the data?",
    "Motivated by the dual nature of adoption-with variation across workplaces depending on their chatbot initiatives and within workplaces depending on individual use-we analyze impacts at both the worker and workplace levels.",
    "Appendix A.2 presents a theoretical framework for how adoption translates into labor market outcomes, guiding the following analyses:",
    "Worker earnings: If AI chatbots raise individual productivity, these gains may translate into higher wages for users (Krueger, 1993)."
  ]
}